name: Glass Style
description:
Textual Inversion Style Embedding trained on glass and crystal. It's an odd one, a little experimental! Sometimes it will give you lovely translucent clothing details, or even clothing made of glass. Sometimes it will give you a shattered effect. Sometimes it will give you glass jars, glass walls, or crystal chandeliers. It also... enhances images. It's not my imagination! Take an old prompt, apply Style-Glass to the front, and see!

Also, this embedding pairs really well with my Style-Psycho - check out some of the example images of the female cyborg!

You can double stack this embedding for even cooler effects - Style-Glass, Style-Glass

Please consider joining my Patreon! Advanced SD tutorials, settings explanations, adult-art, from a female content creator (me!) patreon.com/theally
